<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bqlwb ạlsẖkr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ( bqlwb ạlsẖkr ạlfrḥạnẗ nsjd ljlạlk yạ fạdynạ )2
 ʿly̱ ʿrsẖ qlwbnạ wjwạnạ twjnạ yswʿnạ ʿlnạ
 ạlqrạr - ( bhtạf hạnrnm ạ̉gẖạnynạ whạnʿln mlk yswʿ fynạ ) 2
 2- ( bṣlybk nʿln ạ̹ymạny wklạmk ṣkẖrẗ ạ̹ʿlạnạ )2
 wạlmsḥẗ kfạyẗ tʿlmnạ wbrwḥk trsẖd kẖṭạwynạ
 3- ( bạlrwḥ ạlsạkn fy kyạnạ ạ̹ʿlạnk ywḍḥ qdạmnạ ) 2
 wsẖhạdẗ btrfʿ ạ̉ʿlạmnạ mlkwtk ytḥrk bynạ
 4- ( bạlḥb lḥbk gẖnynạ wạlḥb ạlfạyḍ yrwynạ ) 2
 ạ̉ʿlnt mḥbẗ tkẖlynạ nsẖhd lk mrfwʿẗ ạ̹ydynạ</lyrics>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
